<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-agreements.md" sourcestartlinenumber="64"><a href="rus-inquiries-reports-agreements.html" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-agreements.md" sourcestartlinenumber="64">Inquiries and reports with agreements</a></li>
</ul>
